Installed software products appear in the [Pivotal Cloud Foundry&reg;](https://network.pivotal.io/products/pivotal-cf) (PCF)
Ops Manager Installation Dashboard as clickable tiles, for easy installation. This tutorial explains how to create your own product tile for use in Ops Manager.

